       NOTE: External artifacts such as mq-jms-spring-boot-starter, temporal-spring-boot-starter, 
       and tn3270j are commented out as they are not available in the public Maven Central repository
       configured for this build environment. They would typically be provided via a corporate Nexus 
       or local repo.
    -->
